2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with sports broadcast videos. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper proposes a deep network for regression. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is possible as the paper deals with registering sports field templates onto images. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also possible as the paper deals with finding registration parameters that minimize the regressed error.
